{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"sort","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Element/sort","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath 참고 문서</a></b>: <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 요소</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 함수</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 축</a>\n</div><p></p>\n<p><code>&lt;xsl:sort&gt;</code> 요소는 <code>&lt;xsl:apply-templates&gt;</code>나 <code>&lt;xsl:for-each&gt;</code>가 선택한 노드에 정렬키를 정의하고 노드를 처리할 순서를 결정합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".eb.ac.b8.eb.b2.95","title":"문법","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;xsl:sort\n\tselect=EXPRESSION\n\torder=\"ascending\" | \"descending\"\n\tcase-order=\"upper-first\"| \"lower-first\"\n\tlang=XML:LANG-CODE\n\tdata-type=\"html\" | \"xml\" | \"text\" /&gt; </pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ed.95.84.ec.88.98_.ec.86.8d.ec.84.b1","title":"필수 속성","isH3":true,"content":"<p>없음.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.84.a0.ed.83.9d_.ec.86.8d.ec.84.b1","title":"선택 속성","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect2\">\n  <code>select</code></dt>\n <dd>\n  정렬할 노드를 지정하는 XPath 식을 씁니다.</dd>\n</dl>\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect3\">\n  <code>order</code></dt>\n <dd>\n  \"<code>ascending</code>\"나 \"<code>descending</code>\"으로 처리하면 좋을 노드를 지정합니다. 기본값은 \"<code>ascending</code>\"입니다.</dd>\n</dl>\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect4\">\n  <code>case-order</code></dt>\n <dd>\n  처음에 오는 게 대문자인지 소문자인지를 나타냅니다. 가능한 값은 \"<code>upper-first</code>\"와 \"<code>lower-first</code>\"입니다.</dd>\n</dl>\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect5\">\n  <code>lang</code></dt>\n <dd>\n  어떤 언어를 정렬에 쓸지를 지정합니다.</dd>\n</dl>\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect6\">\n  <code>data-type</code></dt>\n <dd>\n  어떤 항목을 알파벳순이나 숫자순으로 순서 매길지를 정의합니다. 가능한 값은 \"<code>text</code>\"와 기본값인 \"<code>text</code>\"가 있는 \"<code>number</code>\"입니다.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ed.83.80.ec.9e.85","title":"타입","isH3":true,"content":"<p>하위명령, 항상 <code>&lt;xsl:for-each&gt;</code>의 자식으로 나타나고 고유(proper) 템플릿이나 <code>&lt;xsl:apply-templates&gt;</code> 앞에 나타나야 함.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.a0.95.ec.9d.98","title":"정의","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xslt#sorting\" rel=\" noopener\">XSLT section 10, Sorting</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_.ec.a7.80.ec.9b.90","title":"Gecko 지원","isH3":true,"content":"<p>지원함.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"<xsl:sort> 요소는 <xsl:apply-templates>나 <xsl:for-each>가 선택한 노드에 정렬키를 정의하고 노드를 처리할 순서를 결정합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<xsl:sort>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"sort","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<xsl:sort>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/xslt/element/sort","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/xslt/element/sort/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT","title":"XSLT"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Element","title":"Elements"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Element/sort","title":"sort"}],"pageTitle":"sort - XSLT | MDN","noIndexing":false}}